    <item>
      <title>伊朗希望对以色列的报复能够造成伤害，但不会引发更广泛的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/iran-wants-its-israel-retaliation-to-hurt-but-not-start-a-wider-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗面临着一个两难的境地：如何才能对以色列进行有意义的打击，而又不引发席卷中东的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/iran-wants-its-israel-retaliation-to-hurt-but-not-start-a-wider-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 15:26:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密行业的政治捐款也将流向民主党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/crypto-industry-political-donations-are-going-to-democrats-too</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密行业对拜登政府的敌意已导致一些主要参与者公开支持唐纳德·特朗普，该行业通过两个超级政治行动委员会花费数百万美元来干预国会初选，从而塑造民主党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/crypto-industry-political-donations-are-going-to-democrats-too</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约各政治派别民众支持校园手机禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/new-yorkers-across-political-spectrum-back-school-cell-phone-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州选民以压倒性多数支持禁止在课堂上使用智能手机，因为全国范围内越来越多的人担心智能手机会分散学生的学习注意力并危害心理健康。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/new-yorkers-across-political-spectrum-back-school-cell-phone-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:53:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联邦住房贷款银行面临来自拜登政府和参议员的更大压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/fhlbs-face-amped-up-pressure-from-biden-administration-senators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的政府和参议院民主党人正在加大对联邦住房贷款银行系统的压力，要求其投入更多资金解决国家的住房危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/fhlbs-face-amped-up-pressure-from-biden-administration-senators</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:45:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非部长称，南非可在一年内解决港口拥堵问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-can-fix-backlogged-ports-in-a-year-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统府部长 Khumbudzo Ntshavheni 表示，南非港口（位列世界最差之列）的情况正在改善，国有运营商 Transnet SOC 有限公司将在未来 12 到 14 个月内修复这些问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-can-fix-backlogged-ports-in-a-year-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟同意向乌克兰提供 42 亿欧元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/eu-agrees-to-disburse-4-2-billion-of-financing-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟批准向乌克兰提供近 500 亿欧元（550 亿美元）援助计划中的首笔定期付款，旨在帮助乌克兰在俄罗斯入侵期间维持陷入困境的经济运转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/eu-agrees-to-disburse-4-2-billion-of-financing-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:33:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国连锁药店停止购买特斯拉汽车，理由是马斯克支持特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/german-drugstore-chain-rossmann-stops-buying-teslas-citing-musk-s-trump-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国连锁药店 Dirk Rossmann GmbH 将不再购买特斯拉公司的汽车，理由是埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 支持唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/german-drugstore-chain-rossmann-stops-buying-teslas-citing-musk-s-trump-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:25:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是关于蒂姆·沃尔兹和他的政治观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/tim-walz-who-is-kamala-harris-vp-pick-why-did-she-choose-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯选择明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹作为她的竞选搭档，明确表明民主党旨在守住北方各州的“蓝墙”，以阻止共和党人唐纳德·特朗普入主白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/tim-walz-who-is-kamala-harris-vp-pick-why-did-she-choose-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 14:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯邀请明尼苏达州的沃尔兹担任“锈带”竞选搭档</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/tim-walz-is-kamala-harris-vice-president-pick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯任命明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹为她的竞选搭档，并招募他组建沿海和中西部选举联盟，阻止唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/tim-walz-is-kamala-harris-vice-president-pick</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 12:56:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非执政联盟削弱问责制，BOSA 党称</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-s-unity-government-weakens-accountability-opposition-bosa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位选择退出多党联盟的反对党领导人称，南非新的多党政府无意中削弱了该国要求政客为自己的行为负责的能力，因为目前约有 70% 的议员在联盟内任职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-s-unity-government-weakens-accountability-opposition-bosa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:43:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
